id":"4ee033f1b1dbf81a7936cf544b5f9f473338d435","tid":1474073,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"037f78b9a2f1cd03bc3b697bc70cbed437155256","tid":1474073,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"我認我太遲響應連登活動，而家屋企附近恆生細行無哂，atm 都無埋<br />\n星期日出解放軍就仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"一傳話支爆果下已經比人禁曬啦，你會唔會遲左啲阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104c05975797fc520f3e551c208b876ada3d2e47","tid":1474073,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"Guys, my second round <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZBAm4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZBAm4K.png&h=2c92425f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日捉我老母去換埋"},{"pid":"50d47490bc9e79716604e82d061fc6bfd1b051ae","tid":1474073,"uid":103960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9d08e821c6f440dafaa47ce10197e8851ce007a7","tid":1474073,"uid":2404,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4AENuP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4AENuP.jpg&h=04fa2e1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"呢個勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182ad6c19aed2b6bf1b72ee69b6584fba6e5eddb","tid":1474073,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"104c05975797fc520f3e551c208b876ada3d2e47","tid":1474073,"uid":274149,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"Guys, my second round <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZBAm4K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZBAm4K.png&h=2c92425f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日捉我老母去換埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"最緊要叫身邊長輩去換，保住棺材本"},{"pid":"44583e7c3bf09dc54114dff0224d6634f2c888d5","tid":1474073,"uid":307668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"由於開po開錯台，唯有呢度分享。睇咗好多巴打講關於㩒美金嘅文，我都想分享一下睇法，歡迎討論，因為我本身都唔係金融人，亦無讀過經濟金融呢一D科目，所有知識同數據都係靠google 同自己理解，有錯請指點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpgwEmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpgwEmg.jpg&h=ad6d062e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖顯示左香港總共擁有嘅資產，大家可以上金管局搵得返呢啲數據。只有銀行體系總結餘先係現紙，隨時拎到，不用賣出資產或印銀紙。大約有540億港元，呢一個數每一日都會更新。根據統計處3/2019-5/2019，就業人口有3869100，假設呢班人同一日拎錢，即540億除3869100，每人拎得$14029HKD。銀行嘅資金流動性會即時出現問題。你會話邊有咗齊心。咁我又假設200萬人大遊行，唔去遊行而選擇㩒錢或去銀行拎錢，每人拎到$27140。銀行亦會即時出現資金流動問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSBc8hP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSBc8hP.jpg&h=653c5c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，返嚟美金問題，其實就係兩個方法，如上圖顯示，人們可以透過銀行或櫃員機拎錢，咁錢拎到手，只要不在本地消費，錢就不會流入返銀行，銀行就無現錢，相信大家都明白。大家可以選擇擺係屋企衣櫃再用條底褲遮住唔好俾人偷都得，又或者好似一啲巴打所講，申請一個離岸戶口或證券戶口，轉美金入落去或入港紙轉美金，更甚係可以投資外國市場，咁呢舊錢就永遠離開左香港去左外國。亦即係好多人口中嘅走資/撤資。假設呢540真係無曬，咁點算？金管局就需要動用到贖回票據或債券（即係叫啲債仔還錢），又或者動用外匯儲備。根據金管局數據顯示，最新6月外匯儲備有4456.89億美金，需當中有3926.2億美金係投資證券，其餘大多數都就存放在其他國家中央銀行/國際結算銀行/國際貨幣基金組織。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t1Wpe4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft1Wpe4W.jpg&h=d1a3f969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁即係話，一係你追債仔還錢，但未到期，債仔可以唔還住。一係你就沽證券，咁樣就會影響到證券市場，至於呢3900幾億價值嘅證券成份，就沒有公開資料了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWjm1Jr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWjm1Jr.jpg&h=185c4d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你以爲540億現錢好多嘅時候，請看看上圖，上圖顯示左過去19年香港銀行體系總結餘。2008年美國量化寬鬆以來，香港熱錢湧入造成香港島內資金流動性充裕。高峰期去到2015年11月嘅4200幾億，講緊係現錢。之後就一直下降到540億。唔洗4年就唔見左87%。點解會無左咁多？仲記唔記得聞幾年有內地官媒大力吹風話誠仔走資撤資？又咁岩係2015年啵，點走點撤？Well ，留俾大家幻想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6UiZOqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6UiZOqt.jpg&h=9d96f850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖解釋左，當本地貨幣基礎（可理解做銀行結餘）上升就代表資金流入，反之亦然。本地美金貨幣數量有幾多，暫時搵唔到，無得連數。只搵到統計處的流通外幣數量，不好計算。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n金融管理局-市場數據與統計資料：<a href=\"https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/market-data-and-statistics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkma.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fmarket-data-and-statistics%2F&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=f03c8519\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkma.gov.hk/chi/market-data-and-statistics/</a><br />\n<br />\n金融管理局-聯繫匯率制度 CB(1)657/06-07(01) ：<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr06-07/chinese/panels/fa/papers/facb1-657-1-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr06-07%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Ffa%2Fpapers%2Ffacb1-657-1-c.pdf&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=bd4a17b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr06-07/chinese/panels/fa/papers/facb1-657-1-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：GOOGLE IMAGE"},{"pid":"f2e629ca29db2b9826470234e5a51a43b1a18075","tid":1474073,"uid":288014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"瘋狂買iPhone 都不失為一種好方法"},{"pid":"450e33a90e1dfab4dc89a1be16da0dd4ed0b1b98","tid":1474073,"uid":150053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"頭先去咗HSBC ATM睇都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想排隊"},{"pid":"6625b2e9f74fe8be5190c73597f47d72b0eb3119","tid":1474073,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daec12008df844c3dd76bfb81d5e22b26da60ced","tid":1474073,"uid":290911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:16:58.000Z","msg":"去返自己間銀行預約換炒咪得羅，頭先先去渣打預約離，佢唔夠現成現金"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20